Question: Each image appears to contain only zebra-type animals, and in at least one image, the zebras are massed together so its hard to distinguish individual animals.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: https://images.fineartamerica.com/images-medium-large-5/grants-zebras-tanzania-art-wolfe.jpg

Right image URL: https://render.fineartamerica.com/images/rendered/search/canvas-print/mirror/break/images-medium-5/grants-zebra-herd-masai-mara-art-wolfe-canvas-print.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are there only zebra-type animals in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are there only zebra-type animals in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Are the zebras massed together so its hard to distinguish individual animals?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Are the zebras massed together so its hard to distinguish individual animals?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2}')
ANSWER5=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3}')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER4} xor {ANSWER5}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER6)
```
